            <title>[FLINK-5365] Mesos AppMaster/TaskManager should obey sigterm</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5365</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The AppMaster and TaskManager are ignoring the sigterm sent by Marathon/Mesos.   The reason is simply that the shell scripts used to start them don&apos;t pass the signal to java.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
